cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SY, cs.RO 

The paper discusses a machine learning algorithm, specifically a variant of Temporal Difference (TD) learning called Emphatic Temporal Difference (ETD) learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses convergence issues and performance on various experiments, suggesting that it could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also mentions the mountain car prediction problem, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) or cs.RO (Robotics).
